{"tid":2132298,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知前黨友湯家驊望住公民黨被 DQ，有咩感覺呢？","createTime":"2020-07-30T09:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T16:20:26.000Z","uid":7542,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9d66bba9c139f4dfad39ad2362ca755507749b","tid":2132298,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:59:54.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>唔係嘲諷，但真心想知 </strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XZc88k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XZc88k.png&h=c987e811&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wEmCAOm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwEmCAOm.png&h=c5c980d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">2003年湯家驊與梁家傑、余若薇等多名法律界重量級人物組成二十三條關注組</span></strong>，反對特區政府倉促就基本法廿三條立法。及後又組成四十五條關注組，力爭零七零八雙普選。在2005年更與關注組骨幹成員組成公民黨，以推動競爭法、最低工資及普選為目標，亦希望可以促進民主派與中央溝通及合作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊多次撰文反對公民黨參與五區公投，反而加入泛民主派其他政黨如民主黨等所組成的普選聯，以較溫和手段爭取普選。而在民主黨與中聯辦達成協議，決定支持政改方案後，<strong><span class=\"orange\">身為公民黨成員的湯家驊決定跟隨公民黨，投下反對票。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2011年7月，湯家驊<strong><span class=\"orange\">反對把「外傭爭取居港權」事件中的《基本法》條文爭議提請「人大釋法」，認為這會損害法治及司法獨立。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2012年1月，<strong><span class=\"orange\">湯家驊不支持以「人大釋法」或修改《基本法》解決「雙非孕婦來港產子」問題</span></strong>，認為行政手段已經足以打擊有關行為。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然他沒有參與雨傘運動，但湯家驊一直表示他反對方案，會否決政改，拒絕「假普選」。2015年6月18日，28名泛民主派議員，<span class=\"orange\"><strong>包括湯家驊，投票反對政改</strong></span>，由於33名建制派議員在表決前離場，方案被大比數否決。湯在發言時指「今天所有人都是輸家」，並一度哽咽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>2017年7月1日獲時任香港行政長官林鄭月娥委任為香港行政會議非官守成員。</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"5cb94b91751d1765a4246bbe34d9622156291467","tid":2132298,"uid":27416,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:00:39.000Z","msg":"更加堅定相信自己個career path 行得靚"},{"pid":"07ec6832c419eadd4efb551b3dfd81320857147d","tid":2132298,"uid":143499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:01:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db07072c36497074a042e29a8c9d923d454f2afd","tid":2132298,"uid":47042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:01:53.000Z","msg":"都叫爽過最少一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc5a2387e7d82db5086b2b2b1d170b55ff96d00","tid":2132298,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:05:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd2bd2cdca411db46261e977292a3fdf903803d","tid":2132298,"uid":173072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:05:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50613168de61905ebfba37e83d7c0eda0647ba43","tid":2132298,"uid":108347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:06:03.000Z","msg":"佢係布痛腳比人迫轉紅,佢咩感覺都唔會變架啦"},{"pid":"d372d4d1523745bc0ee82babdd371806ab09d295","tid":2132298,"uid":266676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:08:04.000Z","msg":"人地日日食幼女，你識d 咩"},{"pid":"fe9881d73f3dd4484b55f15e39c32f2a8786bce8","tid":2132298,"uid":143230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:20:22.000Z","msg":"公民黨冇成年比佢食<br />\n湯渣：抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef3442f516735b8396b0bd5db39c1bbb0684cd1","tid":2132298,"uid":39383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:33:17.000Z","msg":"湯: 好彩共已投, 唔識果d 人"},{"pid":"d8465df8caf47d3ec7ca9a3bafdb7d9b4822f815","tid":2132298,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T16:18:28.000Z","msg":"比梁家傑採住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=